on my phone in the bathroom.

158
00:06:45,888 --> 00:06:47,706
<i>All right.</i>

159
00:06:47,741 --> 00:06:49,890
All right.

160
00:06:49,943 --> 00:06:52,310
So you pull me into
the ER for what appears

161
