174
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:48,010
Careful not to disrupt
the propeller blade.

175
00:07:48,034 --> 00:07:49,817
Roger that.

176
00:07:49,853 --> 00:07:52,153
- What's her name?
- Becky Copple.

177
00:07:52,188 --> 00:07:54,166
Becky, we're gonna
take care of you, okay?

178
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:55,323
What have we got?

179
00:07:55,358 --> 00:07:57,091
55-year-old male, same accident.

180
00:07:57,127 --> 00:07:58,854
Hit his head on
the deck. No LOC.

181
00:07:58,878 --> 00:08:01,429
GCS 14 on scene for confusion.

182
00:08:01,464 --> 00:08:03,598
I'm fine. Just
please save my wife.

183
00:08:03,633 --> 00:08:05,295
Becky, do you
know where you are?

184
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,934
Hospital.

185
00:08:06,970 --> 00:08:11,005
BP's 75/40, pulse in
the 140s, 02 sat 99%.

186
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,152
