transfusion protocol.

189
00:08:19,182 --> 00:08:21,899
Dr. Feldman, can you
put in a central line?

190
00:08:25,105 --> 00:08:27,672
Oh, there's blood in her pelvis.

191
00:08:27,707 --> 00:08:29,085
The propeller could
be tamponading

192
