227
00:09:53,009 --> 00:09:55,776
Thank you.

228
00:09:57,113 --> 00:09:59,163
I'll be right back.

229
00:10:02,652 --> 00:10:04,163
John and Becky Copple are among

230
00:10:04,187 --> 00:10:05,719
