remove the propeller.

240
00:10:28,712 --> 00:10:30,178
Come on, people, let's move.

241
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,344
Wait, wait. Wh-Wh-Where-where
are they taking her?

242
00:10:35,368 --> 00:10:38,152
