part of the process.

243
00:10:43,359 --> 00:10:46,544
It was my idea to go Jet Skiing.

244
00:10:48,014 --> 00:10:49,431
Becky loves the outdoors.

245
00:10:49,466 --> 00:10:51,799
I hate the sun.

246
00:10:51,834 --> 00:10:54,168
It's one of the few things
we don't have in common.

247
00:10:54,203 --> 00:10:58,055
But this boat came
out of nowhere.

248
00:10:58,091 --> 00:11:00,191
And we crashed at full speed.

249
00:11:00,227 --> 00:11:04,462
I just wish I had gotten
the worst of it and not her.

250
00:11:04,497 --> 00:11:05,997
I can't lose her.

251
00:11:06,032 --> 00:11:09,216
I just...

252
00:11:09,252 --> 00:11:12,520
