00:12:41,777 --> 00:12:44,128
trying to buy us for a
nickel and a rubdown.

294
00:12:44,164 --> 00:12:47,998
But I think we can all agree
that the real winning formula

295
00:12:48,034 --> 00:12:50,968
is not just what's in this
little bottle. No, no, no.

296
00:12:51,003 --> 00:12:52,898
No, it's-it's the
people in this room.

297
00:12:52,922 --> 00:12:56,107
All y'all, the-the men and
brilliant lady right here,

298
00:12:56,142 --> 00:12:58,509
united, working together.

299
00:13:00,179 --> 00:13:01,941
We have struck gold, my
friends, and I don't know,

