324
00:14:05,278 --> 00:14:08,730
And it's only gonna get
worse the longer we wait.

325
00:14:08,765 --> 00:14:10,726
We're gonna have to operate
soon. Any there any issues

326
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:13,262
- that might complicate
his surgery?
