00:23:46,108 --> 00:23:47,575
What the hell happened in there?

517
00:23:47,610 --> 00:23:49,093
I'm replaying it in my head.

518
00:23:49,128 --> 00:23:52,379
This, uh, acute
abdominal pain with nausea

519
00:23:52,415 --> 00:23:54,965
