00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:57,150
but with absolutely no prodrome.

521
00:23:57,186 --> 00:23:59,181
Could he have thrown
a clot to his bowel?

522
00:23:59,205 --> 00:24:01,149
I thought about that,
but nothing on imaging.

523
00:24:01,173 --> 00:24:03,006
And his lactate is flat.

524
00:24:03,042 --> 00:24:03,923
So what's your plan?

525
00:24:03,976 --> 00:24:06,844
Uh, reexamine head to toe.

526
00:24:06,879 --> 00:24:08,456
Rerun labs. Get to
the bottom of this.

527
00:24:10,533 --> 00:24:12,527
Listen, let me know
how I can help you.

528
00:24:12,551 --> 00:24:14,584
They-they took your head.

529
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:16,031
You figured out how
to grow another one.

530
00:24:16,055 --> 00:24:17,582
But don't think for a
second they're not looking

