00:24:25,397 --> 00:24:27,659
And Cain doesn't care that
you brought in Georgia FC.

537
00:24:27,683 --> 00:24:30,167
For him, getting rid
of you is personal.

538
00:24:30,202 --> 00:24:32,452
Be careful.

539
00:24:38,994 --> 00:24:40,627
Buy you coffee?

540
00:24:40,662 --> 00:24:42,596
No.

541
00:24:42,631 --> 00:24:44,615
Please?

542
00:24:44,650 --> 00:24:45,815
Thank you.

543
00:24:45,851 --> 00:24:46,983
Fine.

544
00:24:47,019 --> 00:24:49,319
Uh, one almond
milk latte and one...

